the%20ideal%20family%20consists%20of%20two%20or%20more%20children%2C%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20Gallup%20poll.%3Cp%3ECatherine%20Delahaye%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20annual%20cost%20of%20raising%20a%20kid%20has%20increased%20by%20about%2019%25%20between%202016%20and%202021%2C%20per%20LendingTree.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStill%2C%20most%20Americans%20think%20the%20ideal%20family%20consists%20of%20more%20than%20one%20child%2C%20a%20Gallup%20study%20showed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20the%20ideal%20has%20matched%20up%20with%20people's%20actual%20family%20size%2C%20the%20study%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20Americans%20think%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-marriage-family-structure-kids-over-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bideal%26quot%3B%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%20consists%20of%20more%20than%20one%20child%2C%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gallup.com%2Fpoll%2F511238%2Famericans-preference-larger-families-highest-1971.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGallup%20poll%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20more%20than%202%2C000%20US%20adults%20above%2018%20showed%20that%2089%25%20of%20respondents%20feel%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bideal%20family%20has%20two%20or%20more%20children%20while%20just%203%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20the%20ideal%20number%20of%20children%20is%20one.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20respondents%20either%20said%20zero%20is%20the%20ideal%20number%20or%20they%20have%20no%20opinion%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20breakdown%20of%20what%20people%20say%20is%20the%20ideal%20number%20of%20children%20showed%3A%2044%25%20say%20two%20children%2C%2029%25%20say%20three%2C%2012%25%20say%20four%2C%202%25%20say%20five%2C%20and%202%25%20say%20six%20or%20more%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20doesn't%20go%20into%20what%20reasoning%20the%20re