on%3EDanica%20Roem%2C%20D-Prince%20William%2C%20in%20the%20Virginia%20State%20Senate.%3Cp%3ESteve%20Helber%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDanica%20Roem%20is%20now%20the%20first-ever%20transgender%20state%20senator%20in%20Virginia.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERoem%2C%20who%20previously%20served%20in%20the%20state's%20House%2C%20beat%20her%20Republican%20opponent%20by%20over%203%25%20points.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShe%20hopes%20to%20prioritize%20safe%20transportation%20and%20free%20school%20meals%2C%20among%20other%20goals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELonely%2C%20poor%2C%20and%20quite%20lost%2C%20Danica%20Roem%20thought%20she%20had%20nothing%20going%20for%20her%20back%20in%202016%20except%20toned%20calves%20from%20toting%20kabobs%20up%20the%20stairs%20of%20apartments%20in%20Arlington%2C%20Virginia%2C%20in%20her%20dead-end%20food%20delivery%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPicture%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Roem%2C%20now%20a%20groundbreaking%20politician%20who%20also%20was%20a%20journalist%20back%20then%2C%20wrote%20later%20about%20that%20time%3A%20%26quot%3Ba%20five-foot-eleven%2C%20long-haired%20brunette%20metal-head%20trans%20lady%20reporter%20wearing%20a%20rainbow%20bandana%2C%20an%20A-line%20skirt%2C%20and%20a%20black%20hoodie%20...%20screaming%20obscenities%20behind%20the%20wheel%20of%20her%20four-door%20'92%20Dodge%20Shadow%20America.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20the%20usual%20gauzy%20pitch%20to%20voters.%20But%20in%20Tuesday's%20election%2C%20the%20onetime%20scribe%20and%20heavy%20metal%20singer%20scored%20her%20fourth%20election%20victory%2C%20breaking%20through%20to%20the%20state%20Senate%20and%20overcoming%20a%20pitched%20effort%20from%20Republicans%20and%20their%20allies%20to%20use%20her%20transgender%20identity%20as%20a%20cudgel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20latest%20battles%20in%20America's%20culture%20wars%2C%20Republicans%20across%20the%20country%20tried%20in%20this%20year's%20voting%20to%20make%20the%20embrace%20of%20trans%20rights%20a%20powerful%2C%20emotional%20argument%20against%20Democratic%20candidates%20who%20they%20said%20had%20violated%20social%20norms.%20Against%20Roem%2C%20it%20didn't%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoem%2C%2039%2C%20already%20had%20two%20comfortable%20reelection%20victories%20in%20her%20northern%20Virginia%20House%20of%20Delegates%20district.%20Now%2C%20Roem%20has%20helped%20Democrats%20achieve%20full%20legislative%20control%20in%20an%20election%20that%20broadly%20repudiated%20the%20far%20right%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fvirginia-legislature-election-2023-c928555713fa88b29b0c35f966893f8c%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epromises%20to%20stall%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20socially%20conservative%20agenda%20of%20Republican%20Gov.%20Glenn%20Youngkin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20difference%20between%20this%20campaign%20and%20my%20three%20campaigns%20for%20the%20House%20of%20Delegates%20is%20they%20put%20a%20lot%20more%20money%20into%20promoting%20a%20transphobic%20message%20that%20lost%20as%20opposed%20to%20a%20moderate%20amount%20or%20a%20little%20amount%20of%20money%20into%20a%20transphobic%20message%20that%20lost%2C%26quot%3B%20Roem%20told%20The%20Associated%20Press.%20%26quot%3BThey%20will%20keep%20losing%20by%20doing%20this%20over%20and%20over%20and%20over%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20election%20results%2C%20which%20roundly%20defeated%20Youngkin's%20ideal%20of%20a%20Republican-led%20state%20government%2C%20he%20said%20he%20was%20disappointed%20but%20wanted%20to%20find%20%26quot%3Bcommon%20ground%26quot%3B%20with%20Democrats%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FPolitics%2Fafter-glenn-youngkin-bet-big-virginia-elections-lost%2Fstory%3Fid%3D104720160%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20ABC%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20believe%20there%20is%20a%20place%20we%20can%20come%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Youngkin%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference.%26quot%3BI%20think%20Virginians%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20extreme%20in%20either%20direction.%20I%20think%20in%20the%20long-term%2C%20I%20think%20reasonableness%20is%20where%20people%20will%20come%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20announced%20definitively%20he%20wouldn't%20be%20participating%20in%20the%202024%20presidential%20race%2C%20which%20he%20teased%20for%20months%2C%20per%20ABC%2C%20even%20courting%20billionaires%20as%20potential%20donors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20limited%20races%20in%20the%20off-year%20elections%2C%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20Victory%20Fund%20lists%20148%20openly%20LGBTQ%2B%20candidates%20who%20won%20across%20the%20country%20Tuesday.%20The%20lesson%20from%20this%20%26quot%3Brainbow%20wave%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Annise%20Parker%2C%20the%20fund's%20president%20and%20a%20former%20Houston%20mayor%3A%20%26quot%3BEquality%20wins%20elections%20%E2%80%94%20not%20culture%20war%20scare%20tactics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20electorate%20in%20Virginia%20proved%20less%20interested%20in%20its%20Republican%20candidates%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20focused%20on%20Youngkin's%20proposed%2015-week%20ban%20on%20abortions%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20persuade%20moderate%20voters%20toward%20their%20side.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20coming%20into%20the%20election%20with%20a%20Democratic%20State%20Senate%20and%20a%20Republican%20House%20of%20Delegates%2C%20Virginia%20has%20a%20Democratic%20majority%20in%20both%20chambers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20states%2C%20Democrats%20also%20won%20vital%20battles%20%E2%80%94%20Ohio%20voters%20passed%20a%20constitutional%20amendment%20ensuring%20state%20citizens%20could%20have%20safe%20access%20to%20abortions%3B%20a%20partisan%20seat%20on%20the%20Pennsylvania%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20also%20won%20by%20a%20Democrat%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fballotpedia.org%2FElection_results%2C_2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBallotpedia%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20own%20election%2C%20Roem%20%26quot%3Bfaced%20an%20unprecedented%20deluge%20of%20anti-trans%20hate%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%2C%20but%20she%20was%20not%20fazed%20nor%20distracted%2C%26quot%3B%20Parker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20deluge%20included%20some%2030%20negative%20mass%20mailings%2C%20several%20%26quot%3Bfake%20positive%26quot%3B%20ones%2C%20and%20ads%20accusing%20her%20of%20wanting%20to%20allow%20%26quot%3Bboys%20to%20play%20in%20girls'%20sports.%26quot%3B%20One%20national%20organization%20distributed%20mass%20mailers%20giving%20out%20her%20personal%20cellphone%20number%20and%20imploring%20people%20to%20use%20it%20to%20%26quot%3Bput%20the%20heat%20on%20Danica%20Roem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20flood%20of%20hostile%20callers%20followed%2C%20she%20said.%20Only%20two%20folks%20who%20saw%20the%20mailers%20phoned%20her%2C%20and%20she's%20having%20lunch%20with%20one%20of%20them%20to%20talk%20things%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20other%20side%20decided%20that%20their%20closing%20message%20was%20going%20to%20be%20to%20double%2C%20triple%2C%20and%20quadruple%20down%20on%20transphobia%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20had%20brought%20her%20secret%20sauce%20for%20success%20to%20the%20campaign%2C%20learned%20from%20days%20reporting%20on%20local%20politics%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20what%20office%20you%20run%20for%2C%20always%20run%20like%20you're%20running%20for%20mayor.%20That's%20what%20I%20did.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'Torching%20Doubts'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202016%2C%20Roem%20had%20slept%20in%20more%20than%2060%20parking%20lots%20across%20the%20country%20from%20meandering%20road%20trips%20and%20gigs%20as%20a%20moonlighting%20metal%20rocker%20with%20day%20jobs%20in%20local%20journalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20time%2C%20she%20carefully%20ranked%20the%2040%20best%20lots%20for%20free%20overnight%20parking%2C%20choosing%20a%20Delaware%20rest%20stop%20off%20Interstate%2095%20as%20tops%20because%20of%20the%20always%20open%20bathrooms%2C%20the%20vending%20machines%2C%20and%20lights%20that%20weren't%20too%20bright%20for%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20about%20my%20life%20screams%20'electable'%20(or%20even%20'hygienic')%20on%20paper%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20observed%20in%20her%202022%20memoir%2C%20%26quot%3BBurn%20the%20Page%3A%20A%20True%20Story%20of%20Torching%20Doubts%2C%20Blazing%20Trails%2C%20and%20Igniting%20Change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20she%20had%20caught%20the%20eye%20of%20Democrats%20and%20activists%20in%20her%20frequent%20trips%20to%20the%20Capitol%20in%20Richmond%20to%20advocate%20against%20anti-gay%20bills%20from%20Republicans%2C%20and%20they%20sounded%20her%20out%20about%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20engaging%20a%20variety%20of%20lawmakers%20in%20Richmond%2C%20she%20judged%20the%20deeply%20conservative%20delegate%20from%20her%20own%20district%2C%20Bob%20Marshall%2C%20a%20lost%20cause.%20After%20all%2C%20he%20had%20once%20proudly%20called%20himself%20Virginia's%20%26quot%3Bchief%20homophobe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20lobbying%20him%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Ffaad1d19d35a430ea7ed28ace30ea2c1%2FVirginia-woman-makes-history-as-openly-transgender-delegate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshe%20defeated%20him%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Her%20victory%20in%20a%202017%20House%20of%20Delegates%20race%20made%20her%20the%20first%20openly%20transgender%20candidate%20to%20win%20and%20take%20a%20legislative%20seat%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHer%20Inner%20Mayor%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20trailblazer%20for%20trans%20politicians%2C%20Roem%20is%20celebrated%20in%20Democratic%20and%20cultural%20circles.%20But%20as%20a%20legislator%20with%20a%20solid%20record%20of%20writing%20bills%20and%20getting%20some%20big%20ones%20passed%2C%20she%20is%20known%20for%20her%20passion%20for%20the%20prosaic%2C%20such%20as%20traffic%20congestion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20channeling%20the%20road%20rage%20that%20once%20made%20her%20unleash%20swear%20words%20from%20her%2024-year-old%20Dodge%2C%20Roem%20has%20been%20in%20the%20thick%20of%20the%20debate%20over%20roads%20since%20she%20first%20ran.%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2F953747259b2a44a7bb03819ce5f71e6e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShe%20calls%20Route%2028%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20snaking%20through%20her%20area's%20suburban%20sprawl%20past%20Dulles%20Airport%2C%20an%20obsession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20slogan%20for%20the%202023%20campaign%20was%20%26quot%3BFixing%20roads%2C%20feeding%20kids.%26quot%3B%20Much%20of%20Roem's%20social%20media%20feed%20reads%20like%20a%20transportation%20diary%20%E2%80%94%20or%20the%20work%20of%20a%20mayor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUpdate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%20in%20a%20typical%20post%2C%20%26quot%3Ball%20three%20of%20the%20southbound%20lanes%20are%20now%20all%20open%20in%20Centreville%20from%2029%20to%20just%20before%20the%20Bull%20Run%20bridge%2C%20so%20if%20you're%20taking%20Route%2028%20home%20to%20Manassas%20from%20I-66%2C%20you%20won't%20get%20stuck%20in%20that%20right%20turn%20lane%20in%20front%20of%20the%20movie%20theater.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20pushing%20initiatives%20she's%20already%20fought%20for%20as%20a%20delegate%2C%20she%20pitched%20voters%20on%20improving%20stormwater%20management.%20On%20keeping%20the%20tech%20sector's%20data%20centers%20away%20from%20parks%20and%20homes.%20On%20putting%20new%20transmission%20lines%20underground.%20She%20counts%20Virginia's%20expansion%20of%20Medicaid%20under%20the%20former%20Democratic%20governor%20as%20a%20key%20accomplishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20long%20way%20from%20her%20kabob%20shop%20days%20and%20from%20her%20short-lived%20mobile%20yoga%20studio%20venture%2C%20where%20clients%20did%20their%20moves%20to%20a%20head-banging%20Swedish%20metal%20soundtrack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDigging%20for%20Dirt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20US%20campaigns%20employ%20an%20%26quot%3Bopposition%20research%26quot%3B%20team%20to%20poke%20through%20an%20opponent's%20past.%20In%20her%20first%20two%20campaigns%2C%20Roem%20had%20her%20own%20past%20investigated%20to%20avoid%20being%20blindsided.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20those%20of%20us%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20age%20of%20social%20media%2C%20it%20can%20be%20an%20exercise%20in%20demented%20self-loathing%20to%20figure%20out%20just%20how%20much%20of%20your%20history%20the%20public%20can%20truly%20stomach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESure%20enough%2C%20Marshall's%202017%20campaign%20surfaced%20a%20suggestive%20music%20video%20from%20Roem's%20metal%20band%2C%20Cab%20Ride%20Home.%20%26quot%3BLewd%2C%26quot%3B%20Marshall%20told%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsisting%20on%20calling%20his%20opponent%20by%20male%20pronouns%2C%20he%20also%20played%20up%20Roem's%20comment%20in%20a%20radio%20interview%20when%20asked%20if%20she%20would%20support%20teaching%20kindergarteners%20about%20gender%20identity.%20Yes%2C%20she%20said%2C%20if%20the%20instructions%20were%20age-appropriate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20defeated%20Marshall%20with%2054%25%20of%20the%20vote%20to%20his%2046%25%20and%20posted%20similar%20margins%20in%20the%20next%20two%20elections%20before%20taking%20a%20narrower%20victory%20Tuesday%20over%20a%20former%20police%20detective%2C%20Bill%20Woolf%20III%2C%20with%2052%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20grateful%20the%20people%20of%20Virginia's%2030th%20Senate%20district%20elected%20me%20to%20continue%20representing%20my%20lifelong%20home%20of%20western%20Prince%20William%20County%20and%20greater%20Manassas%2C%26quot%3B%20Roem%20said%20on%20X%20after%20her%20win.%20%26quot%3BThe%20voters%20have%20shown%20they%20want%20a%20leader%20who%20will%20prioritize%20fixing%20roads%2C%20feeding%20kids%2C%20and%20protecting%20our%20land%20instead%20of%20stigmatizing%20trans%20kids%20or%20taking%20away%20your%20civil%20rights.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoem%20rattled%20off%20a%20heavy%20list%20of%20legislative%20priorities%20in%20a%20phone%20interview.%20They%20include%20free%20school%20meals%20for%20all%20public%20school%20students%2C%20earmarking%2010%25%20of%20general%20fund%20surplus%20dollars%20to%20transportation%20safety%20projects%2C%20five%20bills%20to%20control%20data-center%20sprawl%2C%20and%20an%20initiative%20to%20secure%20rights%20for%20people%20to%20be%20buried%20in%20family%20cemeteries%20on%20private%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20chronicled%20her%20sad%20history%20of%20car%20ownership.%20There%20was%20the%20ant-infested%20Subaru%20Outback%20given%20to%20her%20by%20her%20mom%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Balmost%20killed%20me%20twice%20in%20one%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20the%20vehicle.%20And%20the%20%26quot%3Bdirty%20Dodge%26quot%3B%20she%20bought%20from%20her%20drummer's%20dad%20for%20%24700.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20life%20for%20the%20senator-elect%20has%20improved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20driving%20a%20sweet%2C%20sweet%202004%20Nissan%20Sentra%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdanica-roem-anti-trans-critic-state-senate-virginia-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699827669000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655142bf36d588dc55cf234f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdanica-roem-anti-trans-critic-state-senate-virginia-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Roem%20had%20already%20had%20two%20reelections%20in%20her%20northern%20Virginia%20House%20of%20Delegates%20district%2C%20comfortably%20beating%20out%20her%20opponents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sebastian%20Cahill%2CAssociated%20Press)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdanica-roem-anti-trans-critic-state-se