uot%3B%20but%20many%20voters%20have%20been%20miffed%20by%20mainstream%20GOP%20messaging%20on%20an%20issue%20that%20can%20be%20incredibly%20nuanced%2C%20even%20among%20some%20Republican%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeshear%20effectively%20painted%20the%20state's%20near-total%20abortion%20ban%20as%20%26quot%3Bextreme%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20many%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20Mississippi%2C%20the%20abortion%20debate%20was%20essentially%20neutralized%2C%20as%20both%20Reeves%20and%20Presley%20are%20anti-abortion.%20While%20Democratic%20enthusiasm%20for%20Beshear%20may%20have%20been%20amplified%20over%20his%20support%20for%20exceptions%20to%20the%20Kentucky%20law%2C%20the%20opposite%20was%20true%20of%20Presley's%20candidacy%2C%20as%20Mississippi%20Democrats%20were%20likely%20to%20cite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmississippitoday.org%2F2023%2F09%2F28%2Fbrandon-presley-expand-medicaid-tate-reeves%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMedicaid%20expansion%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmississippitoday.org%2F2023%2F09%2F26%2Fbrandon-presley-education-teachers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincreased%20education%20funding%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20core%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERunning%20up%20the%20margins%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeshear%20made%20significant%20inroads%20in%20rural%20and%20suburban%20communities%20across%20Kentucky%2C%20but%20it%20was%20the%20state's%20population%20centers%20that%20powered%20his%20victory%20over%20Cameron.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Louisville%2C%20which%20is%20consolidated%20with%20Jefferson%20County%2C%20Beshear%20won%2070%25%20of%20the%20vote.%20Beshear%20secured%20a%20nearly%20103%2C000-vote%20margin%20in%20Jefferson%20County%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Louisville%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655132c936d588dc55cf223c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBeshear's%20statewide%20margin%20of%20victory%20was%20powered%20by%20cities%20like%20Louisville.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FDavid%20Goldman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELexington%2C%20the%20state's%20second-most%20populous%20city%2C%20is%20consolidated%20with%20Fayette%20County%20and%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20also%20produced%20sizable%20margins%20for%20Democratic%20candidates.%20Beshear%20won%20Fayette%20County%2072%25%20to%2028%25%2C%20a%20huge%2044-point%20edge%20that%20netted%20him%20roughly%2045%2C000%20more%20votes%20than%20Cameron.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBanking%20those%20sorts%20of%20numbers%20was%20helpful%20for%20Beshear%2C%20as%20he%20ran%20competitively%20across%20the%20state%2C%20even%20winning%20several%20counties%20that%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20carried%20by%20large%20margins%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Mississippi%2C%20Presley%20relied%20more%20on%20an%20urban-rural%20coalition.%20He%20campaigned%20in%20suburban%20areas%20as%20well%2C%20but%20the%20state's%20suburban%20voters%20tend%20to%20be%20more%20conservative%20than%20those%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20especially%20in%20northern%20Mississippi%20and%20near%20the%20Gulf%20Coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Presley%20performed%20strongly%20in%20cities%20like%20Jackson%20and%20many%20of%20the%20rural%20counties%20in%20the%20Delta%2C%20the%20margins%20were%20not%20as%20massive%20as%20those%20in%20urban%20Kentucky%20due%20to%20the%20smaller%20population%20sizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Hinds%20County%2C%20home%20of%20the%20state%20capital%20of%20Jackson%2C%20Presley%20beat%20Reeves%2079%25%20to%2020%25.%20But%20Presley's%2059-point%20advantage%20in%20Hinds%20County%20only%20netted%20him%20about%2038%2C000%20votes%2C%20which%20wasn't%20nearly%20enough%20to%20overcome%20Reeves'%20margins%20in%20rural%20and%20suburban%20counties%20across%20much%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20tale%20of%20two%20names%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeshear%20is%20from%20a%20storied%20Democratic%20family%20in%20Ken