.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20complaints%20were%20also%20registered%20at%20the%20Defence%20Colony%20police%20station%2C%20but%20no%20change%20was%20noticed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court's%20firm%20stance%20on%20firecrackers%20got%20blown%20in%20the%20smoke%20of%20the%20firecrackers.%20Despite%20warnings%20and%20a%20complete%20ban...implementing%20authorities%20have%20failed%20yet%20again.%20Wondering%20what%20stance%20will%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20take%20now%3F%20...We%20are%20allowing%20our%20children%20to%20choke%20in%20the%20name%20of%20celebration%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETill%207.30%20pm%2C%20the%20intensity%20of%20bursting%20firecrackers%20was%20less%20in%20Greater%20Kailash%20and%20Chittaranjan%20Park%20area.%20It%20is%20expected%20that%20people%20will%20burst%20firecrackers%20after%20performing%20puja%2C%20people%20in%20the%20locality%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Chhatarpur%20locality%20of%20south%20Delhi%2C%20sounds%20of%20firecrackers%20being%20burst%20could%20be%20heard%20from%206%20pm%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20shopkeepers%20in%20the%20area%20were%20seen%20flouting%20the%20ban%20and%20selling%20small%20firecrackers%20to%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirecrackers%20were%20also%20burst%20by%20some%20people%20in%20south%20Delhi's%20East%20of%20Kailash%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%206%3A30%20pm%20onwards%2C%20intermittent%20noise%20of%20firecrackers%20going%20off%20in%20the%20distance%20could%20be%20heard%20from%20households.%20While%20some%20went%20off%20with%20low%20intensity%2C%20a%20few%20other%20firecrackers%20produced%20booming%20sounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20very%20few%20firecrackers%20were%20burst%20in%20the%20Lalita%20Park%20area%20of%20Laxmi%20Nagar%20till%207%3A30%20pm.%20Locals%20said%20the%20intensity%20may%20go%20up%20later%20in%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20effect%20was%20moderate%20in%20several%20other%20areas%20of%20east%20Delhi.%3C%2