6quot%3BWe%20never%20thought%20we%20would%20have%20to%20argue%20for%20recognition%20of%20our%20own%20humanity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%2C%20which%20was%20formed%20after%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%2C%20condemned%20the%20university's%20initial%20lack%20of%20response%20to%20the%20attacks%2C%20saying%20it%20%26quot%3Bconveyed%20the%20implicit%20approval%20of%20a%20silent%20administration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-ackman-harvard-release-names-students-blaming-israel-violence-hamas-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtroversial%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20signed%20by%2030%20student%20groups%20that%20claimed%20Israel%20was%20%26quot%3Bentirely%20responsible%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20violence%2C%20Harvard%20President%20Claudine%20Gay%20announced%20the%20creation%20of%20an%20advisory%20group%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fview.hu.harvard.edu%2F%3Fqs%3D5899cb44550a82ed4a58f77e66280d2b1e2513ee8ac057c6db942180dd51fb03b3f1bf17aec88eaad543c7f39456498e7782eafe15dc8b336847e59fa4af97f6eda225749f9c983db2fd1a622f969224%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereaffirmed%3C%2Fa%3E%20Harvard's%20%26quot%3Bcommitment%20to%20protecting%20all%20members%20of%20our%20community%20from%20harassment%20and%20marginalization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HCJAA%20acknowledged%20Gay's%20efforts%20but%20outlined%20several%20steps%20that%20it%20still%20wants%20to%20see%20Harvard%20take%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20suggests%20staff%20and%20students%20undergo%20training%20on%20antisemitism%20and%20wants%20to%20see%20plans%20created%20%26quot%3Bto%20ensure%20the%20protection%20of%20Jewish%20students%20on%20campus%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bto%20curb%20the%20dissemination%20of%20hate%20speech.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20suggested%20that%20the%20university%20adopt%20the%20International%20Holocaust%20Remembrance%20Alliance's%20definition%20of%20%26quot%3Bantisemitism.