this%20record%20during%20the%20World%20Cup%20match%20against%20the%20Netherlands%20at%20his%20home%20ground%20of%20M%20Chinnaswamy%20Stadium%20in%20Bengaluru.%20In%20the%20match%2C%20Rahul%20smashed%20102%20in%20just%2064%20balls%2C%20with%2011%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes.%20He%20struck%20runs%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20159.%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20India's%20skipper%20had%20the%20fastest%20WC%20century%20for%20India%20previously.%20It%20came%20in%2063%20balls%20against%20Afghanistan%20in%20this%20tournament%20only%20at%20Delhi.%20In%20nine%20World%20Cup%20matches%20so%20far%2C%20KL%20has%20scored%20347%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2069.40%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%2093.%20He%20has%20scored%20one%20century%20and%20a%20fifty%2C%20with%20the%20best%20score%20of%20102.%20He%20is%20India's%20fourth-highest%20run-scorer%20in%20this%20World%20Cup%2C%20behind%20Virat%20Kohli%20(594)%2C%20Rohit%20(503)%20and%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20(421%20runs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2022%20ODIs%20and%2020%20innings%20this%20year%2C%20KL%20has%20scored%20878%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2067.53%2C%20with%20the%20best%20score%20of%20111*.%20He%20has%20scored%20two%20centuries%20and%20five%20fifties%20this%20year.%20He%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20highly%20dependent%20middle-order%20batter%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20India%20won%20the%20match%20and%20elected%20to%20bat%20first.%20They%20posted%20410%2F4%20in%20their%20fifty%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShreyas%20Iyer%20(128*%20in%2094%20balls%20with%2010%20fours%20and%20five%20sixes)%20and%20KL%20(102)%20led%20India's%20onslaught%20on%20Netherlands.%20But%20knocks%20from%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(61%20in%2054%20balls%20with%20eight%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%20(51%20in%2032%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes)%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20(51%20in%2056%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20laid%20down%20the%20foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBas%20de%20Leede%20(2%2F82)%20was%20the%20leading%20wicket-taker%20for%20the%20Netherlands.%20Paul%20Van%20Meekeren%20(1%2F90)%20and%20Roelof%20van%20der%20Merwe%20(1%2F53)%20also%20took%20a%20wicket%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20needs%20to%20defend%20411%20runs%20to%20complete%20nine%20wins%20in%20nine%20matches%20and%20end%20the%20league%20stage%20on%20high%20and%20the%20Netherlands%20needs%20to%20score%20these%20runs%20to%20secure%20an%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699798920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fkmuid9i8_x_625x300_12_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fkl-rahul-breaks-rohit-sharmas-record-with-sensational-cricket-world-cup-2023-century-4568759%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22KL%20Rahul%20created%20history%20by%20scoring%20a%20brilliant%20century%20during%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20match%20between%20India%20and%20Netherlands.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fkl-rahul-breaks-rohit-sharmas-record-with-sensational-cricket-world-cup-2023-century-4568759%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fkl-rahul-breaks-rohit-sharmas-record-with-sensational-cricket-world-cup-2023-century-4568759%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fkl-rahul-breaks-rohit-sharmas-record-with-sensational-cricket-world-cup-2023-century-4568759%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Muhurat%20Trading%202023%3A%20Sensex%20gains%20355%20pts%20on%201st%20session%20of%20Samvat%202080%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699797279000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2015-11%2F12%2Ffull%2F1447266756-5521.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fmuhurat-trading