.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-67396773%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Treasury-yield%20surge%20boosts%20tokenization%20of%20real-world%20assets%20on%20blockchains%2C%20leading%20'huge%20paradigm%20shift'%20in%20finance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224961%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22crypto%20bank%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63cfecc5a2269e0018c41dce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20Are%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20rise%20of%20Treasury%20yields%20since%202022%20has%20delivered%20a%20major%20boost%20to%20the%20tokenization%20of%20real-world%20assets.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20total%20value%20of%20on-chain%2C%20real-world%20assets%20sits%20at%20%24118.6%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20Fundstrat.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20becoming%20increasingly%20likely%20that%20blockchains%20can%20become%20the%20back-end%20infrastructure%20for%20almost%20every%20asset%20class.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20breathless%20rise%20of%20Treasury%20yields%20since%202022%20has%20delivered%20a%20major%20boost%20to%20the%20tokenization%20of%20real-world%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20US%20bonds%20paying%205%25%20recently%2C%20investment%20firms%20like%20Franklin%20Templeton%20have%20issued%20more%20government%20securities%20on%20the%20blockchain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rising%20interest%20rates%20over%20the%20past%20year%20has%20been%20big%2C%26quot%3B%20Tom%20Couture%2C%20a%20Fundstrat%20analyst%2C%20told%20Insider%2C%20noting%20that%20yields%20in%20decentralized%20finance%20previously%20were%20much%20higher%20than%20for%20US%20bonds.%20%26quot%3BBut%20obviously%20over%20the%20past%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20rates%20have%20gone%20up%20and%20you%20get%20a%20risk-free%205%25%20on%20US%20Treasurys.%20So%20demand%20has%20gone%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20not%20just%20Treasurys.%20There%20is%20a%20growing%20momentum%20around%20packaging%20commodities%2C%20currencies%20and%20investment%20funds%20into%20tokens%20and%20adding%20them%20to%20the%20blockchain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20the%20total%20value%20of%20on-chain%2C%20real-world%20assets%20sits%20at%20%24118.6%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20Fundstrat.%20But%20experts%20say%20that%20number%20is%20expected%20to%20explode.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoston%20Consulting%20Group%20offered%20what%20it%20called%20a%C2%A0%26quot%3Bhighly%20conservative%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb-assets.bcg.com%2F1e%2Fa2%2F5b5f2b7e42dfad2cb3113a291222%2Fon-chain-asset-tokenization.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforecast%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%2416%20trillion%20by%202030%2C%20with%20a%20bullish%20scenario%20putting%20it%20at%20%2468%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20still%20a%20long%20ways%20away%20from%20the%20total%20market%20value%20of%20real-world%20assets%2C%20which%20Fundstrat%20estimates%20is%20more%20than%C2%A0%24992%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20big%20banks%20are%20also%20jumping%20in.%20In%20October%2C%20JPMorgan%20went%20live%20with%20its%20Tokenized%20Collateral%20Network%20%E2%80%94%20a%20system%20that%20allowed%20BlackRock%20to%20tokenize%20one%20of%20its%20money%20market%20funds%20and%20transfer%20it%20to%20Barclays%20in%20a%20derivatives%20trade.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20global%20banking%20network%20SWIFT%20is%20also%20building%20a%20blockchain-based%20system%20for%20financial%20transactions%20with%20the%20tech%20company%20Chainlink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerks%20of%20tokenization%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20tokenization%20is%20not%20new.%20ETFs%20and%20REITs%20are%20earlier%20examples%20putting%20assets%20into%20a%20package%20%E2%80%93%20or%20a%20token.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20tokenization%20of%20real-world%20assets%20onto%20the%20blockchain%20is%20a%20newer%20trend%20that's%20picking%20up%20steam.%C2%A0That's%20because%20investors%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%2C%20it%20helps%20assets%20become%20a%20lot%20more%20liquid.%20When%20an%20asset%20is%20tokenized%2C%20it%20allows%20for%20fractionalization%20%E2%80%94%20divvying%20up%20that%20token%20into%20smaller%20pieces%20%E2%80%94%20which%20improves%20affordability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20a%20token%20on%20the%20blockchain%20can%20be%20traded%2024%20hours%20a%20day%20instead%20of%20the%20seven%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20on%20a%20typical%20stock%20exchange.%20Blockchain%20trades%20also%20have%20faster%20transaction%20speeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20becoming%20increasingly%20likely%20that%20blockchains%20can%20become%20the%20back-end%20infrastructure%20for%20almost%20every%20asset%20class%2C%26quot%3B%20Couture%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20Fundstrat%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EObstacles%20to%20tokenization%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20that%20the%20tokenization%20trend%20hasn't%20leapt%20even%20further%20is%20because%20the%20market%20is%20very%20fragmented%2C%20according%20to%20Lee%20Bratcher%2C%20president%20of%20he%20Texas%20Blockchain%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20tokenized%20government%20securities%20are%20available%20on%20various%20platforms%20instead%20of%20one%20centralized%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20really%20need%20to%20happen%20for%20the%20tokenization%20of%20real%20world%20assets%20to%20take%20off%20is%20for%20an%20entity%20that%20has%20the%20requisite%20licenses%20to%20really%20become%20a%20national%20securities%20exchange%20like%20the%20CME%20for%20commodities%20or%20Nasdaq%20for%20stocks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBratcher%20said%20he%20doesn't%20know%20of%C2%A0efforts%20to%20accomplish%20this%2C%20but%20he%20sees%20a%20national%20exchange%20forming%20in%20as%20soon%20as%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhenever%20it%20happens%2C%20it%20could%2