pital-as-netanyahu-dismisses-calls-for-cease-fire%2Famp_articleshow%2F105164179.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Aware%20of%20States'%20Silencing%20of%20Dissenting%20Voices'%3A%20Academics%20Call%20on%20Turkey%20to%20Cut%20Ties%20With%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F12125115%2Fimage1170x530cropped-4.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Close%20to%20300%20academics%20from%20Turkey%20have%20released%20a%20statement%20in%20support%20of%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20under%20attack%20from%20Israel.%20The%20statement%20highlights%20how%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20attacks%20on%20October%207%20is%20now%20a%20pretext%20for%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20massacre%20of%20Palestinian%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECalling%20themselves%20the%20%E2%80%98Academics%20for%20Peace%20from%20Turkey%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20group%20has%20called%20on%20Turkey%20to%20severe%20all%20military%2C%20commercial%20and%20diplomatic%20relations%20with%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20signatories%20noted%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20actions%20amount%20to%20%E2%80%9Cethnic%20cleansing%20and%20even%20genocide.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20is%20the%20statement%20in%20full%20and%20its%20signatories%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20of%20Israel%2C%20which%20has%20been%20illegally%20occupying%20the%20Palestinian%20territories%20for%2056%20years%20and%20has%20been%20besieging%20Gaza%20since%202006%20in%20violation%20of%20international%20law%2C%20as%20also%20stated%20by%20the%20Secretary-General%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20is%20today%20committing%20another%20crime%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20in%20front%20of%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20whole%20world.%20On%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9CJoint%20Room%20for%20Palestinian%20Resistance%20Factions%E2%80%9D%20consisting%20of%20a%20total%20of%2012%20Palestinian%20organisations%20with%20diverse%20political%20orientations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20often%20reported%20in%20the%20media%20only%20as%20Hamas%20%E2%80%93%20crossed%20the%20Gaza%20border%20and%20killed%20more%20than%201400%20people%2C%20most%20of%20them%20civilians%2C%20with%20air%20and%20ground%20attacks.%C2%A0%20The%20Israeli%20state%20thereupon%2C%20using%20this%20massacre%20almost%20as%20an%20excuse%20or%20even%20%E2%80%9Copportunity%E2%80%9D%2C%20began%20to%20apply%20the%20heaviest%20state%20terror%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20to%20date.%20In%20the%20midst%20of%20these%20massacres%2C%20we%20witnessed%20the%20constant%20bombing%20of%20hospitals%2C%20the%20complete%20destruction%20of%20two%20hospitals%2C%20the%20bombing%20of%20ambulance%20convoys%20and%20the%20open%20declaration%20of%20the%20Israeli%20state%20that%20it%20will%20not%20recognise%20any%20law%20of%20war.%20As%20of%20November%206%2C%20the%20death%20toll%20in%20Gaza%20is%20estimated%20to%20have%20exceeded%2010%2C000%2C%20including%20thousands%20of%20children%20and%20women.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Israeli%20government%20today%20uses%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20recent%20attacks%20as%20a%20pretext%20for%20its%20massacres%2C%20but%20we%20know%20that%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%20intense%20repression%20and%20violence%20by%20the%20Israeli%20security%20forces%20even%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20Hamas.%20The%20Israeli%20government%2C%20which%20has%20been%20labelled%20an%20apartheid%20regime%20by%20many%20Jewish%20diaspora%20initiatives%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20well%20as%20by%20political%20and%20civil%20initiatives%20of%20Israeli%20citizens%2C%20implies%20in%20front%20of%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20world%20that%20it%20aims%20to%20wipe%20out%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%2C%20estimated%20at%202.2%20million%2C%20from%20the%20face%20of%20the%20earth.%C2%A0%20The%20land%20operation%20launched%20by%20Israel%2