e%20truism%20that%20all%20Hindus%20are%20not%20equal%2C%20be%20it%20in%20social%20clout%20or%20economic%20well-being.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20catch%2022%20that%20disables%20desired%20right-wing%20majoritarian%20homogeneity%20thus%20visibly%20resides%20in%20the%20false%20consciousness%20of%20that%20claim%20of%20unity%2C%20a%20reality%20that%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESanatan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20leadership%20is%20able%20neither%20to%20deny%20nor%20to%20embrace.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20classical%20Marxist%20parlance%2C%20the%20concrete%20yet%20again%20trounces%20the%20attempted%20abstract.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20what%20does%20the%20too-clever-by-half%20numero%20uno%20do%20to%20counter%20the%20telling%20gulfs%20between%20discrete%20Hindu%20social%20groups%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20goes%20Marxist%2C%20not%20in%20any%20considered%2C%20classical%2Fideological%20way%20%E2%80%93%20perish%20the%20thought%20%E2%80%93%20but%20in%20an%20instantly%20put-on%2C%20bleeding-heart%20expansiveness%2C%20which%20is%20tactical%2Fpolemical%20to%20the%20finger%20nail.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Ergo%2C%20Shri%20Modi%2C%20%E2%80%9Cclose-%20bosom%20friend%E2%80%9D%20(to%20borrow%20a%20phrase%20from%20John%20Keats)%20of%20private%20corporate%20India%2C%20(selectively%2C%20as%20we%20know)%20declares%20in%20yet%20another%20thundering%2C%20impromptu%20flourish%20at%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20poll-bound%20Chhattisgarh%20that%20there%20is%20but%20one%20caste%20alone%20in%20Bharat%2C%20and%20that%20comprises%20%E2%80%9Cpoor%E2%80%9D%20Indians.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E(Never%20mind%20that%20he%20cannily%20leaves%20no%20opportunity%20to%20lest%20us%20know%20that%20he%20is%20the%20first%20Other%20Backward%20Class%20prime%20minister%20of%20the%20republic.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20is%20not%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20followed%20up%20that%20acknowledgement%20of%20Indian%20poverty%20with%20a%20daring%20estimate%20as%20well%3A%2081%20crore%20Indians%20(roughly%20some%2060%25%20of%20the%20population)%20fall%20into%20the%20category%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpoor%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20a%20computation%20that%20beggars%20all%20previous%20estimates%20of%20poverty%20figures%20by%20sundry%20experts%2C%20and%20rather%20piquantly%20endorses%20the%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%20determination%20(2023)%20which%20lists%20India%20at%20111%20out%20of%20125!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20then%2C%20rather%20thoughtlessly%20again%2C%20went%20on%20to%20declare%20that%20he%20had%20decided%20that%20this%20only%20caste%2C%20namely%2C%20%E2%80%9Cpoor%E2%80%9D%2C%20Indians%2C%20would%20continue%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fin-another-sign-of-deep-economic-distress-modi-says-free-ration-to-800-million-to-continue%5C%22%3Ereceive%20the%20bounty%20of%20free%20rations%20for%20all%20of%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fin-another-sign-of-deep-economic-distress-modi-says-free-ration-to-800-million-to-continue%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Efive%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fin-another-sign-of-deep-economic-distress-modi-says-free-ration-to-800-million-to-continue%5C%22%3E%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20clearly%20assuming%20that%20he%20is%20set%20to%20return%20to%20power%20in%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20here%20is%20the%20funny%20part%3A%20this%20declaration%20has%20embedded%20in%20it%20the%20further%20confession%20that%20the%20current%20poverty%20rate%20as%20now%20acknowledged%20by%20him%2C%20is%20set%20to%20remain%20undiminished%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20self-confessed%20tribute%20to%20the%20governance%20of%20the%20Modi-led%20right-wing%2C%