2023-11-10-09-53-04-826.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684470%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EConstables%20on%20duty%20at%20Sapna%E2%80%99s%20house.%20Photo%3A%20Omar%20Rashid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20family%20was%20targeted%2C%20says%20Sapna%2C%20because%20she%20had%20refused%20to%20withdraw%20a%20sexual%20harassment%20complaint%20she%20lodged%20against%20the%20men%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20later%20arrested%2013%20men%20for%20the%20brutal%20murder%20of%20her%2018-year-old%20younger%20brother%20and%20also%20booked%20them%20under%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESapna%20and%20her%20mother%20are%20still%20disturbed%20by%20the%20violence%20that%20transpired%20on%20August%2024.%20They%20fear%20the%20worst%20if%20the%20BJP%20returns%20to%20power%20in%20the%20central%20Indian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHum%20bachenge%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Enahi%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%5BWe%20won%E2%80%99t%20survive%5D.%20We%20will%20be%20compelled%20to%20leave%20our%20house%20and%20locality%20if%20the%20BJP%20returns%20to%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sapna%2C%20seated%20on%20a%20cot%20outside%20her%20house%20that%20faces%20a%20barren%2C%20rocky%20patch%20of%20land.%20She%20believes%20that%20if%20the%20BJP%20forms%20the%20government%20again%20in%20MP%2C%20she%20will%20not%20get%20justice%20and%20might%20have%20to%20face%20backlash%20from%20the%20accused%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20as%20well%20as%20the%20opposition%20Congress%20party%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20main%20accused%20persons%20in%20the%20case%20were%20linked%20to%20Bhupendra%20Singh%2C%20a%20powerful%20minister%20in%20the%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan-led%20BJP%20government%20and%20the%20MLA%20from%20the%20Khurai%20assembly%20seat%2C%20under%20which%20the%20village%20falls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20will%20go%20to%20assembly%20polls%20next%20week%2C%20has%20the%20unflattering%20record%20of%20being%20the%20state%20with%20the%20worst%20crime%20rate%20against%20Dalits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20compiled%20by%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20shows%20that%20the%20state%20recorded%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fnationalcrimerecordsbureau%2Fpost%2F1679310741CII2021Volume2.pdf%5C%22%3Ecrime%20rate%20(per%20lakh%20of%20the%20population)%20of%2063.6%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20members%20of%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20in%202021.%20The%20national%20average%20for%20the%20year%20was%2025.3.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmanoj-mitta-caste-based-violence-impunity-interview%5C%22%3EManoj%20Mitta%20on%20Why%20Caste-Based%20Violence%20Continues%20With%20Impunity%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%2C%20which%20has%20been%20under%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20BJP%20for%20almost%20two%20decades%2C%20also%20recorded%20high%20crime%20rates%20against%20Dalits%20in%202019%20and%202020%20(46.7%20and%2060.8)%20against%20national%20averages%20of%2022.8%20and%2025%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalits%20form%20roughly%2016%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20and%20though%20scattered%2C%20are%20an%20important%20voting%20segment%20in%20the%20backward%20regions%20of%20Bundelkhand%20and%20the%20Chambal-Gwalior%20belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20has%20regularly%20targeted%20the%20BJP%20whenever%20cases%20of%20atrocities%20against%20Dalits%20are%20reported%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20issue%20has%20not%20been%20a%20major%20part%20of%20its%20election%20campaign%2C%20which%20has%20mostly%20focused%20on%20welfare%20schemes%20and%20general%20issues%20such%20as%20unemployment%2C%20corruption%20and%20socio-economic%20guarantees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20election%20manifesto%2C%20the%20party%20promised%20to%20review%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20SC%2FST%20Act%20in%20the%20state%20and%20said%20that%20cases%20lodged%20under%20the%20law%20would%20be%20investigated%20by%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20rank%20of%20additional%20superintendent%20of%20police%2C%20if%20it%20was%20voted%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20that%2C%20atrocities%20against%20Dalits%20have%20hardly%20been%20a%20talking%20point%20for%20the%20two%20main%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20insecurity%20felt%20by%20the%20Dalit%20family%20in%20Barodiya%20Nounagir%20offers%20a%20snapshot%20of%20the%20isolation%20felt%20by%20the%20victims%20of%20alleged%20caste-based%20atrocities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20is%20the%20dread%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20MLA%20that%20even%20the%20Dalit%20neighbours%20of%20the%20family%20are%20unwilling%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20brutal%20murder%20and%20atrocity%20suffered%20by%20them%2C%20even%20though%20they%20are%20sympathetic%20in%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Sapna%20was%20allegedly%20molested%20by%20the%20accused%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20alleged%20that%20the%20accused%20persons%20linked%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%20minister%20were%20putting%20pressure%20on%20her%20to%20reach%20a%20compromise.%20And%20on%20the%20evening%20of%20August%2024%20this%20year%2C%20three%20persons%20named%20Komal%20Singh%20Thakur%2C%20Azad%20Thakur%20and%20Bikram%20Thakur%20barged%20into%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20house%20and%20threatened%20Sapna%20and%20her%20mother%2C%20who%20were%20at%20home%2C%20with%20dire%20consequences%20if%20they%20did%20not%20withdraw%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Arun%20Yadav%20had%20in%20August%20shared%20a%20letter%20on%20social%20media%20which%20showed%20that%20one%20of%20the%20accused%20men%2C%20Komal%20Singh%20Thakur%2C%20was%20a%20nominated%20representative%20of%20BJP%20minister%20Bhupendra%20Singh%2C%20who%20holds%20the%20urban%20development%20and%20housing%20portfolio%20in%20the%20outgoing%20government.%20Komal%20Singh%20was%20also%20the%20husband%20of%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Barodiya%20Nounagir%20gram%20panchayat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98We%20will%20not%20allow%20you%20to%20live%20in%20the%20village.%20We%20will%20beat%20you%20and%20chase%20you%20away.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20you%20have%20love%20for%20your%20children%3F%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20told%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Munni%20Devi%2C%20Sapna%E2%80%99s%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMunni%20Devi%20still%20wears%20a%20white%20bandage%20on%20her%20right%20arm%2C%20which%20has%20long%20and%20dark%20stitch%20marks%20from%20her%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F10202955%2Fsignal-2023-11-10-09-51-54-942-1024x768.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F10202955%2Fsignal-2023-11-10-09-51-54-942-1024x768.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F10202955%2Fsignal-2023-11-10-09-51-54-942-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F10202955%2Fsignal-2023-11-10-09-51-54-942.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684471%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Omar%20Rashid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20threatening%20Sapna%20and%20Munni%20Devi%2C%20the%20accused%20men%20intercepted%20Sapna%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20who%20was%20returning%20from%20the%20market%2C%20and%20allegedly%20thrashed%20him%20brutally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTwo%20of%20their%20men%2C%20Golu%20Soni%20and%20Lalu%20Khan%2C%20grabbed%20him.%20They%20beat%20us%20up%20too%20when%20we%20inte