k-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20showcased%20environmental%20responsibility%20by%20unveiling%20national%20flags%20crafted%20from%20recycled%20PET%20bottles.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334072%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20showcased%20environmental%20responsibility%20by%20unveiling%20national%20flags%20crafted%20from%20recycled%20PET%20bottles.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20bring%20these%20exceptional%20flags%20to%20life%2C%20approximately%2011%2C000%20PET%20bottles%20were%20used%20to%20create%20each%20national%20flag%2C%20while%20approximately%202%2C000%20PET%20bottles%20were%20utilised%20for%20each%20ICC%20unity%20flag.%20The%20flags%20were%20skillfully%20manufactured%20by%20GoRevise%20%E2%80%94%20a%20division%20of%20Ganesha%20Ecoverse%20Limited%20%E2%80%94%20which%20specialises%20in%20the%20production%20of%20recycled%20yarn%20and%20garments.%20Over%20100%20dedicated%20workers%20contributed%20their%20time%20and%20effort%2C%20working%20tirelessly%20for%2025%20days%20and%20clocking%20over%20300%20hours%20to%20produce%20these%20flags.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20thrilled%20to%20announce%20Coca-Cola%20India%20%E2%80%94%20partnering%20with%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Go%20Rewise.%20Together%2C%20we%20have%20made%20history%20at%20the%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20by%20unveiling%20the%20National%20Flags%20of%20each%20country%20participating%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%20ICC%20Unity%20Flag.%20These%20flags%20are%20a%20first%20in%20cricket%20worldwide%2C%20made%20entirely%20from%20Recycled%20PET%20bottles.%20India%20is%20celebrating%2C%20and%20we%20at%20Go%20Rewise%20are%20equally%20delighted%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20this%20incredible%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20%3Cstrong%3ESandeep%20Khandelwal%2C%20Vice%20President%2C%20Ganesha%20Ecosphere%20and%20Managing%20Director%2C%20Ganesha%20Ecoverse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoca-Cola%20India%20initiated%20both-%20online%20and%20offline%20(on-ground)%20initiatives%20throughout%20the%20tournament%2C%20aimed%20at%20engaging%20fans%20and%20consumers%20and%20raising%20awareness%20about%20waste%20management.%20The%20Company%20is%20facilitating%20waste%20management%20as%20part%20of%20the%20%23MaidaanSaaf%20campaign%20and%20has%20installed%20reverse%20vending%20machines%20at%20all%20the%20stadiums%20for%20the%20collection%20of%20consumed%20PET.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArnab%20Roy%2C%20Vice%20President%2C%20Marketing%2C%20Coca-Cola%20India%20%26amp%3B%20Southwest%20Asia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20expressed%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CCoca-Cola%20has%20a%20mission%20to%20support%20sustainability%20efforts%20as%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20all%20sporting%20events.%20Aligned%20with%20this%20mission%2C%20we%20take%20pride%20in%20unveiling%20national%20flags%20made%20with%20recycled%20PET%20at%20the%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20today.%20With%20these%20recycled%20national%20and%20ICC%20unity%20flags%20we%20are%20dedicated%20to%20advancing%20the%20principles%20of%20a%20circular%20economy.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20the%20significance%20of%20sports%20and%20cricket%20in%20the%20hearts%20of%20millions%20in%20India%2C%20Coca-Cola%20India%2C%20and%20ICC%20intend%20to%20showcase%20their%20commitment%20to%20creating%20a%20sustainable%20sporting%20experience%20during%20this%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699677000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FCocaCola_ICC_Ground_11zon-1699628770.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334067%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Celebrating%20the%20shared%20passion%20for%20cricket%20and%20a%20dedication%20to%20sustainability%2C%20Coca-Cola%20India%20and%20ICC%20unveiled%20national%20flags%20crafted%20from%20post-consumer%20PET%20bottles%2C%20making%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20tournament%20a%20platform%20for%20promoting%20environmental%20responsibility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Pranita%20Bhat%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334067%2Ficc-mens-cricket-world-cup-coca-cola-unveils-national-flags-made-from-recycled-pet-bottles%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Photo%20Essay%20%7C%20An%20Evening%20in%20West%20Bank's%20Susiya%2C%20Battling%20the%20Threat%20of%20Israeli%20Settler%20Terror%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F09211644%2FFeatured-photo.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20it%E2%80%99s%20Susiya%E2%80%99s%20turn.%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwp.me%2Fp4H68Q-33X%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMu%E2%80%98arrajat%3C%2