ainst%20your%20country%2C%20be%20brave%20enough%20to%20stand%20for%20it%20and%20correct%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Asha%20%3Cem%3Esan%20%3C%2Fem%3Etells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20in%20her%20frail%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20Asha%20restarted%20her%20education%20and%20got%20married%20in%201949.%20While%20she%20engaged%20herself%20in%20volunteer%20works%2C%20her%20contribution%2C%20like%20many%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F190053%2Fgulab-kaur-woman-freedom-fighter-punjab-independence-day-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen%20freedom%20fighters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Tanvi%20believes%2C%20remained%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F129013%2Fnetaji-subas-chandra-bose-death-conspiracies%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetaji%E2%80%99s%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20most%20of%20the%20records%20were%20destroyed.%20So%2C%20not%20many%20know%20the%20contribution%20of%20the%20INA%20and%20this%20young%20girl%20in%20the%20Indian%20freedom%20movement%20in%20East%20Asia.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20INA%20members%20came%20to%20India%20that%20Indian%20citizens%20got%20to%20know%20about%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20regiment%20in%20Japan%20and%20how%20these%20women%20fought%20for%20freedom.%20We%20only%20know%20about%20a%20handful%20of%20female%20freedom%20fighters%20despite%20them%20being%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20read%20such%20personal%20stories%20of%20war%2C%20it%20makes%20you%20understand%20what%20people%20went%20through%20and%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20a%20country%2C%20that%20was%20nurtured%20by%20the%20sacrifices%20of%20people%2C%20for%20granted.%20Her%20story%20is%20inspirational%20for%20young%20women.%20For%20%3Cem%3Edadi%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eit%20was%20only%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20that%20people%20started%20giving%20her%20recognition.%20This%20book%20has%20gotten%20some%20attention%20to%20her%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanvi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20even%20went%20the%20extra%20mile%20to%20collate%20various%20photographs%20and%20letters%20written%20in%20classic%20Japanese%20language%20and%20the%20INA%20archives%20to%20put%20together%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Tanvi%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20bedtime%20stories%20are%20centered%20around%20Asha%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20freedom%20movement.%20Her%20children%20take%20pride%20in%20singing%20%3Cem%3EKadam%20Kadam%20Badhaye%20Ja.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Tanvi%20Srivastava.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699626225000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334021%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20Netaji%20Bose%2C%20Asha%20Sahay%20was%2017%20when%20she%20joined%20INA's%20Rani%20of%20Jhansi%20regiment%20and%20fought%20for%20Indian%20independence.%20Her%20great-granddaughter-in-law%2C%20Tanvi%20Srivastava%2C%20has%20documented%20her%20incredible%20story%20in%20the%20book%20'The%20War%20Diary%20of%20Asha-san'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IIT%20Madras%20NPTEL-GATE%20Portal%20Offers%20Free%20Resources%20to%20Prepare%20for%20the%20Exam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20Madras%20is%20offering%20the%20NPTEL-GATE%20portal%20to%20students%20aspiring%20to%20ace%20the%20GATE%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Programme%20on%20Technology%20Enhanced%20Learning%20(NPTEL)%20%E2%80%94%20Graduate%20Aptitude%20Test%20in%20Engineering%20(GATE)%20portal%20provides%20access%20to%20previous%20years%E2%80%99%20questions%20from%202007%20to%202022%2C%20covering%20various%20exam%20topics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20institution%E2%80%99s%20press%20statement%20notes%20that%20every%20year%2C%20about%20seven%20to%2010%20lakh%20students%20in%20India%20take%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F217007%2Fgate-exam-topper-tips-akhand-swaroop-pandit-postgraduation-engineering-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGATE%20examination%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20in%202023%2C%20about%20seven%20lakh%20students%20registered%2C%20and%20about%20one%20lakh%20students%20successfully%20qualified.%20The%20exam%20preparation%20programme%20on%20the%20portal%20has%20seen%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20student%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20online%20platform%20has%20received%20over%2050%2C700%20registrations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThings%20to%20know%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20NPTEL-GATE%20portal%20offers%20all%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F229119%2Fiit-madras-free-online-course-nptel-registration-date-how-to-apply-india-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeatures%20for%20free%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBetween%20August%202022%20and%20February%202023%2C%20students%20completed%20115%20mock%20tests%20across%20six%20key%20subjects%20%E2%80%94%20electrical%20engineering%2C%20mechanical%20engineering%2C%20civil%20engineering%2C%20electronics%20and%20communication%2C%20physics%2C%20and%20chemistry.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20current%20semester%20started%20on%2015%20October%2C%202023.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%2019%20mock%20tests%20were%20completed%20across%20seven%20subjects%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20six%20mentioned%20above%20in%20addition%20to%20biotechnology.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp